{
  "stem": "24195.6",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And the five of us, which was a mistake-- we were much too big a group-- we tried to get up, work our way up to the forest that was the-- before the opening where the border-- which was not really marked.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You just had to assume there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You know, there were no-- really no guards.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I mean, every so often there was a guard house, every maybe every mile or every kilometer or something like this.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yeah, the war-- that's, that's August of 1945, yeah.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so we go, we go on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we-- we're waiting in a, in a, in a forest, at the edge of the forest, to cross that opening, that big field-- on, on the other side is the Americans zone-- while the morning fog is on.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And standing there about 4:00.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was August, so daybreak starts early.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We're starting to walk across, actually running.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We have knapsacks on our, on our backs, when the fog lifts.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, and the, and the Russian patrol spots, spotted us and started shooting, yelling to, to stop, to halt.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We don't do this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We start running toward the forest, hoping we will get away and get lost in the forest.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But they were-- it was foolish, really.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because they were shooting after us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the bullets were whizzing around all.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But they were bad shots.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So-- but they were better runners, so they caught up with us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they brought us back to the command post near the zone border, near the-- on the Russian side.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And there, we had to go through the routine again, Showed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Our papers.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The, the officer in charge let us go, but with a stern warning, you have to go back to Berlin.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There's no agreement.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
